analysis: The documents in this cluster all pertain to executive orders related to domestic policy. They cover a range of topics including domestic manufacturing, artificial intelligence infrastructure, national security and emergency preparedness communications, delegation of presidential authorities, Iran sanctions, foreign assistance, migratory bird conservation, intelligence activities, and regulation of petroleum commerce and energy resources. Despite the variety of topics, a common thread is the use of executive authority to address perceived national needs and priorities.
title: Domestic Policy & Executive Action
